							<div class="post_wrapper author">
								<div id="about_the_author">
									<div class="gravatar"><a href="https://lithub.com/author/andrewmartin/"><img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screen-Shot-2020-07-07-at-8.07.46-PM-100x100.png" width="100" height="100" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Screen-Shot-2020-07-07-at-8.07.46-PM-300x298.png 2x" alt="Andrew Martin" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></a></div>
									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/andrewmartin/">Andrew Martin</a></h6>
										Andrew Martin is the author of the novel <em>Early Work</em>, the story collection <em>Cool for America</em>, and the forthcoming novel <em>Down Time</em>.																			</div>
